headline: Senators demand US trade chief Tai halt late talks on investor protections
summary: A bipartisan group of U.S. senators on Wednesday called on U.S. Trade Representative Katherine Tai to stop secret negotiations with Mexico, Canada and Colombia that would weaken investor protections...
